      "effect": "This card's Level is increased by 4 during your opponent's turn only. You can only use each of the following effects of \"Metal Copycat\" once per turn. If this card is Normal or Special Summoned: You can Set 1 \"Metalmorph\" Trap directly from your Deck, then, if you have \"Enhanced Metalmorph\" in your GY, you can draw 1 card. You can declare 1 Monster Type; this card becomes that Type until the end of your opponent's turn.",
